OL,5, Jobs on the railways "will need to     
OL,6, change to become more                  
OL,7, passenger-centric", according to the   
OL,8, group that represents train operators. 
OL,10,FThe Rail Delivery Group (RDG) was      
OL,11,Fresponding to reports that hundreds of 
OL,12,Frail ticket offices could potentially  
OL,13,Fclose as part of a plan to modernise   
OL,14,Fthe railways.                          
OL,16,FRDG said it is talking to unions about 
OL,17,Fhow to address job changes.            
OL,19,FOne union said it will ballot staff if 
OL,20,Fcompulsory redundancies are used.      
